@startuml Google_Vision_Processing_Flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor white

start
:Prepare PDF Page Images;
note right: Multiple PNG files\nNatural sorting (page_001.png, etc.)

:Initialize Google Vision Client;
note right: declare_key.py\nService account authentication\nAPI key management

:Process Images in Batch;
note right: main.py\nLoop through all images\nError handling for each file

:Call Vision API;
note right: DOCUMENT_TEXT_DETECTION\nHigh accuracy OCR\nDocument structure analysis

:Extract Full Text;
note right: response.full_text_annotation\nPreserve text layout\nHandle multi-language content

:Save as UTF-8 Text File;
note right: output_txt_dir/filename.txt\nOne text file per image\nProgress tracking

:Generate Processing Report;
note right: OK/NG statistics\nCharacter count per file\nError logging

stop

@enduml